---
title: Thai-Style Chicken & Creamy Slaw Bowl with Sweet Chilli Sauce & Coriander
description: It’s a good idea to have an extra layer on you, but how about on tonight’s dinner? Let’s add layers upon layers of flavour by crusting the chicken in pumpkin seeds, our Aussie spice blend and golden breadcrumbs for a crunchy texture. Cook it up and serve with a tangy aioli.

